{"tid":821671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打風食罐頭，等唔等同中秋食月餅？端午節要食傻一樣？","createTime":"2018-09-16T04:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T04:46:10.000Z","uid":124859,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"770a24aedfe4648bc27b3d217e232f4938c49576","tid":821671,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:29:09.000Z","msg":"如果屋企冇一日以上嘅糧食，你去買，OK<br />\n如果你本身屋企有足夠嘅糧食，都仲要成班豬咁樣走去搶，驚死洩底，就係自私<br />\n有冇諗過一啲屋企本身唔足夠糧食，但又夜收工既人？就係俾你班豬搶晒<br />\n<br />\n我屋企一家三口，有一日足夠糧食<br />\n已有兩包公仔麵同叮點心<br />\n由頭到尾咩柒都無買過<br />\n我屌你老母成班港豬有冇諗過真正需要嘅人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ca98d5c20b1fb7713f195da00ed1bbd63b6226","tid":821671,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"民智未開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7eb08ea0895739223d1770559431d289165f4d0","tid":821671,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9186c7b13c12221aeb493eef02af7e5f7519e715","tid":821671,"uid":143288,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f7eb08ea0895739223d1770559431d289165f4d0","tid":821671,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:45:22.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"27aa1e4b8771325a708df2692c92a7ccfa059cd2","tid":821671,"uid":116497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7eb08ea0895739223d1770559431d289165f4d0","tid":821671,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}